00230 typedef struct
00231 {
00232         // Two or three letter language code
00233         char language[4];
00234 
00235         // Two or three letter country code (Sometimes with Cyrl_ prefix)
00236         char country[10];
00237 
00238         // 32-bit unsigned integer corresponding to the locale
00239         unsigned int code;
00240 
00241 } locale;
